    "Below is a buggy function. Fix it so that it works correctly:\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "def buggy_function(x, y):\n",
    "    if x > y\n",
    "        print(\"x is larger\"\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        return y\n",
    "```"
   ]
